{"tid":1365252,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"26/7 機會集會「和你飛」必須和理非","createTime":"2019-07-25T14:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:28:15.000Z","uid":127618,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"777155b065a688e0cbca6a02fc01517bd61b849b","tid":1365252,"uid":127618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xSwd4WK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxSwd4WK.png&h=f656178d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7a12dP4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7a12dP4.png&h=610e6124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提提大家今次集會必須<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今次集會係面向全世界 比遊客知道 比遊客睇到<br />\n更重要係為之後可能既罷工試水温 打下強心針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場特警唔係講笑 佢可以無預警下開槍去維護機場以至航空安全 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />況且你係走唔到 機場之所以得兩條橋出入就係萬一有恐襲 可以方便隔離恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以唔該大家 機場入面必須<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冷靜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實機場入面都好多聲音想為今次運動出一分力 <br />\n但機場入面加班文化係根深蒂固 <br />\n我地底薪低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多有家室既人靠加班先生活到<br />\n好多人都面對好現實手停口停既問題<br />\n<br />\n如果今次做得好 清晰向世界各地遊客表達香港現狀同訴求 表現到公民質素 罷工就可以埋下種子<br />\n<br />\n大家試想像如果....<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">冇空姐同空姐哥哥<br />\n冇人上貨同行李<br />\n冇人為機倉清理<br />\n冇人維修飛機<br />\n冇人指揮航空交通</span><br />\n所帶來既個影響係衝擊所達唔到！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">天佑香港！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fMFiwFh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfMFiwFh.png&h=e8496c43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2180c38c14aa336c2c2021c8af4968da0167b6f2","tid":1365252,"uid":127618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"屌 好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打錯標題"},{"pid":"91f1feaf173bf4519120600685bb38b4e79f15b5","tid":1365252,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:00:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c9292443c58c3869a4f00b46e71f7d460c7e4e0","tid":1365252,"uid":35192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:13:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b9a332fc878b05f2309661e4cbbc77507a7a25a","tid":1365252,"uid":78414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"請大家推上環義士情況，元朗鄉黑文宣post<br />\n中共用鄉黑警搞恐怖襲擊、<br />\n上環黑警開槍諗住殺義士<br />\n文宣要做足<br />\n重申五大訴求<br />\n連儂牆、傳單，放映會<br />\n宣傳727，召集民防隊<br />\n<br />\n726 機場<br />\n727 元朗<br />\n728 上環"}]}